body:
So yeah, I'm pretty much done with minecraft, it's just been getting really boring and nothing is fun anymore.

I've moved on to csgo and this is my final post or whatever...

Most of you guys probably know me as 26763/numbers, I'm was one of those guys that had numbers as their name.


People that made a change to my life:

PokerFace: 
You motivated me to lead the Predators Team which was something that changed my life, I can't imagine my life without it. You brought me up when I was feeling down and gave me hope when I had none. You told me to keep going cause you'll never know what will happen if yo don't try. I'll miss you man, in the long run, good luck with life, you always have my skype so, yeah.


Jozzmcozz/FluenZa/Whatever his name is now (I'm pretty lost with the name changing):

Thanks for teaching me how to play this game properly :P I still suck compared to you at every game, it was fun, when I kept getting destroyed by you in CoD/kohi, and me always begging for a re-match, MR PLANE MAN PLEASE STOP THE BOMBING RUNS!1!!!!1!one!!111eleven1!!!!!11!!!


Much more but eh, don't have time right now.

BYE
